Perturbation parameters for count variables

params_cnts.Rd

This object is a result from [ck_params_cnts())] and is used in unit-tests.

[ck_params_cnts())]: R:ck_params_cnts())

Format

params_cnts: a ck_params object that can be used as input in cellkey_pkg() and contains parameters to perturb count variables

References

https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/cros/content/3-random-noise-cell-key-method_en
